cpu-tweaks (0.2.0) noble; urgency=low

  * Initial PPA release.
  * Auto-detects Intel P-State, AMD P-State, acpi-cpufreq drivers.
  * Governor, EPP, frequency limits, turbo boost controls.
  * Live per-core frequency bars with 5s auto-refresh.
  * Drift detection warns when settings don't match system state.

